&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own a mission-critical product charter at scale.&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;PubMatic is one of the world&#39;s largest independent supply-side platforms (SSPs), and we&#39;re looking for an Associate Director of Product to lead a core area within our Monetization organization.&lt;/li&gt;
