&lt;p&gt;Are you interested in leading a market and shaping the future of AI‑driven digital advertising?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an opportunity to lead PubMatic’s Central European business (DACH &amp;amp; Poland) at an important stage in our evolution. With strategic and commercial responsibility, you will define the growth agenda for one of our key EMEA regions, combining local market ownership with the backing of a global, publicly listed AdTech organisation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will play a visible role in supporting our transition to an AI‑powered, data‑driven technology business, bringing advanced solutions to market and contributing to the continued evolution of programmatic advertising.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are motivated by impact, innovation, and building sustainable growth in a fast‑moving and competitive environment, this role offers the opportunity to lead and scale a high‑potential region.&lt;/p&gt;
