&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;text-start &quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lead new business development and strategic account growth across publishers, agencies, and buyers. By balancing market expansion with long‑term partnership development, you will help unlock new revenue streams and strengthen PubMatic’s regional position.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;text-start &quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Partner cross‑functionally with Product, Marketing, Customer Success, and Legal to bring AI‑driven capabilities and data solutions to market in a compliant and client‑focused way.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;text-start &quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Drive operational excellence across the region, supporting strong execution, effective pipeline management, accurate forecasting, and high levels of client satisfaction through data‑informed decision making.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;text-start &quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Represent PubMatic within the regional industry ecosystem, contributing to discussions on AI and the future of digital advertising while fostering a collaborative, inclusive, and high‑performing team environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
